---
title: Turkey & Gouda Brioche Sandwiches with Dijonnaise, Lettuce & Tomato
description: This is a far cry from your average ho-hum turkey and cheese sammy (although it still takes just 10 minutes to make). We’ve hooked you up with soft, plush brioche buns, hearty sliced turkey, and mild, nutty gouda slices. Simply whip up a quick homemade Dijonnaise to slather on the buns, layer with crisp baby lettuce and juicy tomato, and dig into a classic yet elevated sandwich you’ll look forward to all morning.
